                <head>No. 322.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Brigham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Consulate</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Paso del Norte</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1886-07-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 22, 1886</date>. (Received July
                        23.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mexico massing troops at this point: 150 men this morning, and 2,000 said to be
                    on the way. Cutting still in prison. Great excitement.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>BEIGHAM,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Consul.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
